{"tid":1322154,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"柏林連儂牆","createTime":"2019-07-16T00:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T23:30:42.000Z","uid":281031,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2ed783dde925b002dcba18a165c7e340f21ca2","tid":1322154,"uid":281031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:53:05.000Z","msg":"【連儂牆遍地開花@柏林圍牆遺址】<br />\n<br />\n1989年，香港人透過電視機見證柏林圍牆倒下；今天，在柏林圍牆，我們聽見香港人的聲音，看到港人熟悉的風景&mdash;&mdash;連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n沿途不少德人駐足，有人拿起紙筆，寫下「Eier gegen Wand」，意指「雞蛋與高牆」，亦有留言支持香港守護法治、香港不是中國等德語字句。現場有不少德人表示一直關注香港事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n今晚港人經歷新城市一役，也許這不是個絕好的時機，但是在德國的港人想告訴大家，世界正在注視香港，請不要放棄，民主總會戰勝。<br />\n<br />\nLennon Wall Blossoms on Berlin Wall<br />\n<br />\nHongkongers watched on TV as the Berlin Wall fell in 1989. Today, Hongkongers&rsquo; voice is heard where the Wall used to be. Lennon Wall messages spread on the Berlin Wall. Locals and tourists stopped to read and write messages - messages like &lsquo;Eier gegen Wand&rsquo; (eggs against wall), &lsquo;Unsere Justizsystem sch&uuml;tzen&rsquo; (protect our judiciary), and &lsquo;Hongkong ist nicht China&rsquo; (Hong Kong is not China). Passers-by said they had been paying heeds to the situation in Hong Kong. <br />\n<br />\nIt might be the darkest time yet, but Hongkongers in Germany would like to send their support home to their comrades - the world is watching and democracy shall prevail. Hang in there! <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3e2q6h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3e2q6h.png&h=9c940ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/16/085010_a6b1a67331be8c31dc9d745644597958.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2F085010_a6b1a67331be8c31dc9d745644597958.png&h=212db544&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/16/085012_e817ad8cfbc609aaefbe0180ff19a6fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2F085012_e817ad8cfbc609aaefbe0180ff19a6fd.png&h=a10724f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/16/085014_bf8b8485112f6fd2401befe1cac8c6aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2F085014_bf8b8485112f6fd2401befe1cac8c6aa.png&h=2baa4c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/16/085016_f4c2d17d3a486232175853765af2f89b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2F085016_f4c2d17d3a486232175853765af2f89b.png&h=e3505620&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/16/085019_f5ed3a78d13321d4b3526c79e0f2f8a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2F085019_f5ed3a78d13321d4b3526c79e0f2f8a9.png&h=9f9c17c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/16/085020_fa02444c7a0d8aafab1d105483d9098c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2F085020_fa02444c7a0d8aafab1d105483d9098c.png&h=dc1bb02f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf41f50d8aab6f30f8cde93554782dd248cb8718","tid":1322154,"uid":69986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:35:15.000Z","msg":"仲以為係柏林SIR俾人貼滿香港連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856dc458d16c850402a219aebe91ae0cabf23f31","tid":1322154,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf41f50d8aab6f30f8cde93554782dd248cb8718","tid":1322154,"uid":69986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:35:15.000Z","msg":"仲以為係柏林SIR俾人貼滿香港連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"same"},{"pid":"e553667862d4ad1a